Datasets published to the Haemdata pin board

Source: R/metadata.R
published_pins.Rd

Lists the name and version of each dataset published to the Haemdata pinboard in the current release. Pins can be retrieved with the get_pin() function.

Usage

data(published_pins)

Format

A data.frame with the following columns:

pin_name

Name of the dataset on the pin board, including the file extension

version

Version of the pin to which the dataset belongs

Examples

published_pins |> knitr::kable()
